# Git workflow (NexFit365)

Follow the **branch-pr-deploy** skill (`.cursor/skills/branch-pr-deploy/SKILL.md`).

- Do not commit feature/fix work on `main`.
- Create `feat/`, `fix/`, `chore/`, or `docs/` branches from `main`.
- Push and open a PR for every change set.
- Merge the PR only when the user asks to deploy (or explicitly to merge).
- After merge: `git pull origin main`, then `./deploy.sh --background`.
- Track branch/PR/task in `.agents/state.md` (local, gitignored).
